reviews.review_text:
Solid AUD While there is an official release and a variety of boot boards, it's nice to get the audience perspective once in a while. My brother-in-law and I were at the blue line, just behind center ice, down low in the risers. There were some huge biker guys behind us who were puffing down. After the lights came up, we were speechless. Nevertheless, we made eye contact with our burly neighbors, and they simply said, "Wow, Dark Star."

35 years later(!), this show holds water. The Mattes / Miller team on this recording make for a nice ambient experience with more dynamics than the board in many ways. What it lacks in pinpoint precision it makes up for warmth. Dig it.
